<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>管理系统API服务</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #409EFF;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #67C23A;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .endpoints {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .endpoints h2 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #606266;
        }
        .endpoint {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 4px solid #409EFF;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>管理系统API服务</h1>
        <p>后端服务器已成功启动！</p>
        <div class="status">运行中</div>
        <p>服务器时间: {{serverTime}}</p>
        <p>API版本: v1.0</p>
        
        <div class="endpoints">
            <h2>可用API端点:</h2>
            <div class="endpoint">GET / - API服务首页</div>
            <div class="endpoint">POST /api/auth/register - 用户注册</div>
            <div class="endpoint">POST /api/auth/login - 用户登录</div>
            <div class="endpoint">GET /api/auth/me - 获取当前用户信息</div>
            <div class="endpoint">GET /api/products - 获取产品列表</div>
            <div class="endpoint">GET /api/orders - 获取订单列表</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>